title: Veggie Time - Veg Out Time
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Chinese, Indian, Thai, Buffet, Fast food, Take-out, Asian
description: In late-2013, Veg Out Time moved from 63A Fitzroy St to this spot and modified its name to Veggie Time. Look for the green signage with a red "V." Casual space. Offers menu of Asian vegetarian and vegan food. There is a steamtable of cooked dishes on display where you could pick and choose what you'd like.
